            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="11448426">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">信息泛滥的互联网使人变得习惯于浅阅读，失去深度思考的能力。收集信息不等于知识。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/11448426/">(<span class="">2回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
