            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="12954132">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">成功等于3%聪明才智+97%抵御互联网干扰。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/12954132/">(<span class="">2回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
